import React from 'react'; import data from './headArray.json'; /** * @return {boolean} */ export default function Table ({fires}) { const body = fires.map((fire, i) => { return {fire.id} {fire.date} {fire.message} {fire.addressObjectFireFeature} {fire.district} {fire.fireStation} {fire.object1} {fire.object2} {fire.rescueWorks} {fire.amountOfRescuedPeople} {fire.amountOfEvacuatedPeople} {fire.fireChiefRank} {fire.fireChiefName} {fire.amountOfSmokeGroups} {fire.smokeTime} {fire.extinguishingAgents} {fire.firstEngine} {fire.secondEngine} {fire.thirdEngine} {fire.firstReserve} {fire.secondReserve} {fire.firstSquadron} {fire.secondSquadron} {fire.hydrant} {fire.reportPDF} {fire.locality} {fire.fireRank} {fire.detectionTime} {fire.messageTime} {fire.arrivalTime} {fire.firstNozzleTime} {fire.localizationTime} {fire.fireLiquidationTime} {fire.totalLiquidationTime} {fire.comment} }); const head1 = (fires) => { return ( {fires.map(fire => (fire.data))} ) }; const head = data.map((column, j) => { return {column.id} {column.date} {column.message} {column.addressObjectFireFeature} {column.district} {column.fireStation} {column.object1} {column.object2} {column.rescueWorks} {column.amountOfRescuedPeople} {column.amountOfEvacuatedPeople} {column.fireChiefRank} {column.fireChiefName} {column.amountOfSmokeGroups} {column.smokeTime} {column.extinguishingAgents} {column.firstEngine} {column.secondEngine} {column.thirdEngine} {column.firstReserve} {column.secondReserve} {column.firstSquadron} {column.secondSquadron} {column.hydrant} {column.reportPDF} {column.locality} {column.fireRank} {column.detectionTime} {column.messageTime} {column.arrivalTime} {column.firstNozzleTime} {column.localizationTime} {column.fireLiquidationTime} {column.totalLiquidationTime} {column.comment} }); return ( {head} {head1}
); }
